<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.5.3">
<l>āyaṉ māyamē yaṉṟimaṟ ṟeṉkaiyil vaḷaikaḷu miṟainillā</l>
<l>pēyi ṉāruyi ruṇṭiṭum piḷḷainam peṇṇuyirk kiraṅkumō</l>
<l>tūya māmatik katirccuṭat tuṇaiyillai 	yiṇaimulai vēkiṉṟatāl</l>
<l>āyaṉ vēyiṉuk kaḻikiṉṟa tuḷḷamumañ cēleṉpā rilaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[Even] without the herder’s trickery, still the bangles on my arms</l>
<l rend="indent">will not stay for a second.</l>
<l>Will the child who consumed the dear life of the demoness</l>
<l rend="indent">feel pity for the lives of us girls?</l>
<l>When the rays of the pure, great moon scorch me, there is no help!</l>
<l rend="indent">Both of my breasts are indeed blazing!</l>
<l>Even [my] heart is faltering for the herder’s flute; there is no one who says,</l>
<l rend="indent">“Don’t fear.”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
